videos.headline: Warren gives Cincy the early lead with a rushing TD
videos.description: Michael Warren II goes up the middle and into the end zone for a six-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Warren gives Cincy the early lead with a rushing TD) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Gibson bursts through the hole for a 65-yard TD
videos.description: Memphis running back Antonio Gibson runs through the hole and takes off for a 65-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gibson bursts through the hole for a 65-yard TD) 2019/12/09

videos.headline: Memphis forces fumble after Ridder's long run
videos.description: Cincinnati quarterback Desmond Ridder takes off for a big gain but is stripped by Chris Claybrooks, giving Memphis the ball.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ridder is stripped by Claybrooks giving Memphis the ball) 2019/12/07

videos.headline: Ridder keeps it and finds the end zone for the TD
videos.description: Desmond Ridder keeps it on the option and strolls into the end zone for the 15-yard touchdown.
